prodNameC: 羅氏可霸斯免疫分析雌二醇檢驗試劑
ingredientsDesc:
Reagent - working solutions：
M   Streptavidin-coated microparticles (transparent cap), 1 bottle, 6.5 mL: Streptavidin-coated microparticles 0.72 mg/mL; preservative.
R1  Anti-estradiol-Ab~biotin (gray cap), 1 bottle, 8 mL: Biotinylated polyclonal anti-estradiol  antibody (rabbit) 45 ng/mL; Mesterolon 130 ng/mL; MES buffer 50 mmol/L, pH 6.0;      preservative.
R2  Estradiol-peptide~Ru(bpy) (black cap), 1 bottle, 8 mL: Estradiol derivative, labeled with ruthenium complex 2.75 ng/mL; MES buffer 50 mmol/L, pH 6.0; preservative.

CalSet – working solutions：
• E2 II Cal1: 2 bottles, each for 1.0 mL of calibrator 1
• E2 II Cal2: 2 bottles, each for 1.0 mL of calibrator 2
Estradiol (synthetic) in two concentration ranges (approx. 73 pmol/L or 20 pg/mL and approx. 11,000 pmol/L or 3000 pg/mL) in a human serum matrix.
